org.springframework.session.data.gemfire.serialization.data.support

Class DataSerializerSessionSerializerAdapter<T extends org.springframework.session.Session>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.geode.DataSerializer
      • org.springframework.session.data.gemfire.serialization.data.AbstractDataSerializableSessionSerializer<T>
        • org.springframework.session.data.gemfire.serialization.data.support.DataSerializerSessionSerializerAdapter<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SessionSerializer<T,java.io.DataInput,java.io.DataOutput>

    @Component
public class DataSerializerSessionSerializerAdapter<T extends org.springframework.session.Session>
extends AbstractDataSerializableSessionSerializer<T>
    The DataSerializerSessionSerializerAdapter class is a two-way Adapter adapting a SessionSerializer instance as an instance of DataSerializer in a GemFire/Geode context, or adapting a DataSerializer as a SessionSerializer in a Spring Session context.
    Since:
    2.0.0
    See Also:
    DataSerializer, Session, SessionSerializer, WirableDataSerializer, Component
